Actually, let me be more precise with the derangement calculation:
$$D_{12} = 12! \times \sum_{i=0}^{12} \frac{(-1)^i}{i!}$$

The exact value of the sum is approximately 0.367879441.

$12! = 479001600$

$D_{12} ≈ 176214841$

$12^{12} = 8916100448256$

